Kim Myers https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kim_Myers 0 Kimberly S. Myers (born February 15, 1966) is an American television and film actress. Her breakthrough role was in the 1985 horror film A Nightmare on Elm Street 2: Freddy's Revenge as Lisa Webber. She acted in another horror sequel in 1996, Hellraiser: Bloodline. Myers is married to producer/writer Eric Small. Kimberly_S._Myers ( born February_15_,_1966 ) is an_American_television_and_film_actress .
